<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 18:08:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>你需要知道的第 167 天：美国起草联合国停火决议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-167-u-s-drafts-un-resolution-for-cease-fire/0000018e-61f9-d66c-a7fe-65fb91cd0000</link><description>以色列安全官员不顾哈马斯和总理内塔尼亚胡的反对，推动计划招募与哈马斯无关的巴勒斯坦领导人来分发加沙援助。 以色列国防军：600名恐怖分子在希法医院被捕。 美国起草了一项联合国决议，呼吁“立即停止火灾与释放人质有关 ■ 众议院议长迈克·约翰逊表示，他计划邀请内塔尼亚胡向国会发表讲话 ■ 战争结束 167 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 18:01:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-167-u-s-drafts-un-resolution-for-cease-fire/0000018e-61f9-d66c-a7fe-65fb91cd0000</guid></item><item><title>游客可能不喜欢特拉维夫的新城市博物馆，但它不适合他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tourists-may-not-like-tel-avivs-new-city-museum-but-its-not-for-them/0000018e-5781-d2a6-adef-d7d7763a0000</link><description>在特拉维夫旧市政厅改建的博物馆中，当地人有机会对第一个现代希伯来城市的传说产生怀疑，而邻近的雅法在每一个展览中都有发言权。即使是 Nakba 也没有被掩盖起来</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 17:55:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tourists-may-not-like-tel-avivs-new-city-museum-but-its-not-for-them/0000018e-5781-d2a6-adef-d7d7763a0000</guid></item><item><title>新调查显示，犹太裔美国人和穆斯林美国人在以色列-加沙战争问题上存在明显分歧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/sharp-fault-lines-among-jewish-and-muslim-americans-over-gaza-war-new-survey-reveals/0000018e-61ff-d507-a1cf-63ff27b50000</link><description>调查显示，大多数美国人认为以色列打击哈马斯的理由是合理的，但相信以色列在加沙战争中的行为将使以色列人更加安全的人要少得多</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 17:26:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/sharp-fault-lines-among-jewish-and-muslim-americans-over-gaza-war-new-survey-reveals/0000018e-61ff-d507-a1cf-63ff27b50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的哈斯巴拉正在失败。那是好消息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-hasbara-is-failing-thats-good-news/0000018e-61b1-d66c-a7fe-65b3c7f50000</link><description>多年来，内塔尼亚胡让以色列人相信，原话比战略更重要，油嘴滑舌的借口比自我反省或实质内容更重要。加沙战争暴露了对哈斯巴拉的信仰已成为一种负担</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 17:20:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-hasbara-is-failing-thats-good-news/0000018e-61b1-d66c-a7fe-65b3c7f50000</guid></item><item><title>来自耶路撒冷的 MAGA 参议员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/the-maga-senator-from-jerusalem/0000018e-618c-dde2-a5df-7bed7e9b0000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡不擅长民主、国家安全和外交关系，但他擅长一件事：破坏美国在以色列问题上宝贵的两党合作</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 16:37:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/the-maga-senator-from-jerusalem/0000018e-618c-dde2-a5df-7bed7e9b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列可以而且必须在不让加沙平民挨饿的情况下与哈马斯作战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-can-and-must-fight-hamas-without-starving-gazan-civilians-to-death/0000018e-6014-d411-a3df-f0dedd910000</link><description>以色列向加沙提供粮食援助的缓慢行为是不合情理的：这无异于折磨平民，甚至让长期的朋友也变成了震惊的批评者。但以色列可以在不帮助哈马斯的情况下减轻这种不必要的痛苦</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 14:40:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-can-and-must-fight-hamas-without-starving-gazan-civilians-to-death/0000018e-6014-d411-a3df-f0dedd910000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷将举行普林节游行，尽管加沙人质亲属请求取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-to-hold-purim-parade-despite-gaza-hostages-relatives-plea-to-cancel-it/0000018e-6115-d092-afcf-79d72d040000</link><description>加沙人质的家人称耶路撒冷选择扣留阿德洛亚达“缺乏敏感性和团结”，并指责其是出于经济动机。该市否认，称他们的目的是给该市的孩子们带来快乐的经历，“这场战争的一些英雄”</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 14:29:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-to-hold-purim-parade-despite-gaza-hostages-relatives-plea-to-cancel-it/0000018e-6115-d092-afcf-79d72d040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列预备役士兵杀死了不构成威胁的62岁巴勒斯坦男子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-reserve-soldier-kills-62-year-old-palestinian-man-who-posed-no-threat/0000018e-60f6-d702-a58e-68f7bd900000</link><description>宪兵将调查在以色列国防军地区防御营服役的预备役士兵，该营由招募来保护西岸定居点的定居者组成</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 12:58:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-reserve-soldier-kills-62-year-old-palestinian-man-who-posed-no-threat/0000018e-60f6-d702-a58e-68f7bd900000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院命令国家允许将两名母亲列入孩子的出生证明上</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/high-court-orders-state-to-allow-two-mothers-to-be-listed-on-childs-birth-certificate/0000018e-60c4-d03d-a7ff-e1e78c860000</link><description>针对八年前九对女同性恋夫妇提交的请愿书，高等法院裁定，对同性伴侣子女的出生证明进行任何区别“可能会发出一种冒犯性的信息，即这些关系在本质和质量上是不同的”</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 12:31:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/high-court-orders-state-to-allow-two-mothers-to-be-listed-on-childs-birth-certificate/0000018e-60c4-d03d-a7ff-e1e78c860000</guid></item><item><title>“一片混乱”：在加沙，以色列国防军使用了 70 年前用于训练的弹药和炮弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/a-huge-mess-in-gaza-idf-used-70-year-old-munitions-and-shells-intended-for-training/0000018e-5db4-d4b2-afcf-dfb626a90000</link><description>试图将弹药、非正规货物和“印度炸药”保存在分解的麻袋中，造成了后勤和行动上的噩梦，使炮兵部队难以协助作战部队，并增加了出错和错过目标的风险</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 12:20:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/a-huge-mess-in-gaza-idf-used-70-year-old-munitions-and-shells-intended-for-training/0000018e-5db4-d4b2-afcf-dfb626a90000</guid></item><item><title>如果加沙儿童挨饿，以色列将永远失去道德合法性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/if-gazas-children-starve-israel-will-lose-its-moral-legitimacy-forever/0000018e-5c96-d3c4-a7cf-7dd6e7720000</link><description>“儿童已开始死于明显的饥饿”：如果以色列继续在加沙发动战争，同时阻碍大规模粮食援助的提供，它将被视为现代记忆中最严重的人道主义危机之一的主要根源</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 12:06:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/if-gazas-children-starve-israel-will-lose-its-moral-legitimacy-forever/0000018e-5c96-d3c4-a7cf-7dd6e7720000</guid></item><item><title>拜登计划停止拉法行动并提醒内塔尼亚胡：以色列需要美国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/biden-plans-to-halt-the-rafah-op-and-remind-netanyahu-israel-needs-america-more-than-ever/0000018e-5e8d-d4b2-afcf-de9fa5760000</link><description>尽管与美国关系紧张，总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡仍继续谈论“全面胜利”，但他派遣代表团前往华盛顿的事实凸显了两国之间的力量平衡</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 04:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/biden-plans-to-halt-the-rafah-op-and-remind-netanyahu-israel-needs-america-more-than-ever/0000018e-5e8d-d4b2-afcf-de9fa5760000</guid></item><item><title>摩萨德负责人率领的以色列代表团周五前往卡塔尔进行人质和停火谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article-live/idf-chief-at-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-operation-seeks-to-pressure-hamas-on-hostages/0000018e-5ebb-d27e-a7af-7effa02c0000</link><description>以色列国防军和辛贝特称，超过 600 名恐怖分子在 Al-Shifa 医院被捕，其中包括哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战组织高级官员 ■ 五角大楼负责人敦促以色列重新考虑拉法地面行动，寻求其他选择 ■ 内塔尼亚胡告诉参议院共和党人，即使以色列必须进入没有美国支持的拉法“我们不会停止” ■ 布林肯会见沙特外长，讨论“保护加沙所有平民的迫切需要”</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 02:04:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article-live/idf-chief-at-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-operation-seeks-to-pressure-hamas-on-hostages/0000018e-5ebb-d27e-a7af-7effa02c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列21岁以下国家足球队自1976年以来首次参加奥运会就发现了对手</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-national-soccer-team-discovers-opponents-in-first-olympic-appearance-since-1976/0000018e-5d68-d411-a3df-ddfacfca0000</link><description>21岁以下国家队将对阵巴拉圭、马里和一支尚未确定的亚洲球队。教练盖伊·吕宋 (Guy Luzon)：“能够成为 48 年来第一支代表以色列参加重大赛事的球队，真是令人兴奋”</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 00:34:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-national-soccer-team-discovers-opponents-in-first-olympic-appearance-since-1976/0000018e-5d68-d411-a3df-ddfacfca0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登的红线：拉法为何成为美以政治战场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/bidens-red-line-why-rafah-has-become-a-political-battleground-between-the-u-s-israel/0000018e-5dd5-d092-afcf-7dd7a46d0000</link><description>无论是否发生，仅仅以色列国防军袭击拉法的幽灵就为内塔尼亚胡提供了至关重要的政治资本。拜登政府正中他下怀</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 00:13:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/bidens-red-line-why-rafah-has-become-a-political-battleground-between-the-u-s-israel/0000018e-5dd5-d092-afcf-7dd7a46d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院介入阻止国家将巴勒斯坦癌症患者送回加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-steps-in-to-stop-state-sending-palestinian-cancer-patients-back-to-gaza/0000018e-5e32-d27e-a7af-7efe67c40000</link><description>以色列国防官员希望将患者及其亲属送回加沙地带，尽管担心他们在那里无法得到适当的治疗。高等法院下令暂停该计划，直至听取反对此举的请愿书</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 00:02:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-steps-in-to-stop-state-sending-palestinian-cancer-patients-back-to-gaza/0000018e-5e32-d27e-a7af-7efe67c40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在约旦河西岸发动两次空袭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/idf-air-strike-on-four-terrorists-in-jenin-including-two-top-islamic-jihad-operatives/0000018e-5e2a-d27e-a7af-7eee3ff30000</link><description>艾哈迈德·巴拉卡特是以色列在杰宁和努尔沙姆斯难民营空袭中丧生的人之一，以色列国防军称他去年对赫尔梅什实施了枪击袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 23:27:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/idf-air-strike-on-four-terrorists-in-jenin-including-two-top-islamic-jihad-operatives/0000018e-5e2a-d27e-a7af-7eee3ff30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院史无前例地允许拆除非致命袭击恐怖分子的家庭住宅</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-okays-demolition-of-family-home-of-terrorist-behind-non-fatal-attack/0000018e-5db5-d4b2-afcf-dfb728ec0000</link><description>当场被杀的 Khaled Al-Mohtaseb 的家人就拆除令向法院请愿，称他们没有参与导致一名边境警察受重伤的袭击事件</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 23:17:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-okays-demolition-of-family-home-of-terrorist-behind-non-fatal-attack/0000018e-5db5-d4b2-afcf-dfb728ec0000</guid></item><item><title>数十名美国前高级官员敦促拜登：如果以色列阻止加沙援助，请考虑限制美国对以色列的援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/former-officials-urge-biden-mull-restricting-assistance-to-israel-if-it-blocks-gaza-aid/0000018e-5e0f-d4b2-afcf-de9f4cf60000</link><description>近70名美国前国家安全高级官员和外交官敦促美国总统采取更有力的措施，促进人道主义准入和保护加沙平民</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/former-officials-urge-biden-mull-restricting-assistance-to-israel-if-it-blocks-gaza-aid/0000018e-5e0f-d4b2-afcf-de9f4cf60000</g